Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再見吧 金牛座
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯迪巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鈞一髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界之樹的內部？
