Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.30,0:22:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我知道的全都告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:22:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒我一條小命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說 神鬥士在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這山谷的深處
